source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000005_NOPHICA<tab>At last, the time is come!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000005_NOPHICA<tab>ああ  とうとうこのときが来た……！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000030_MENPHINA<tab>Come bathe in the moon's tender glow!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000030_MENPHINA<tab>さあ  月神の愛で満たしてあげる！

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000040_MENPHINA<tab>Our dreams may yet become reality. Thank you.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06301_000040_MENPHINA<tab>ありがとう
